{"tid":111551,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"識揀一定唔會揀夢露絲打做女友","createTime":"2017-02-07T13:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T16:27:01.000Z","uid":65818,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f6fc636f26464445d5dcf679870a94d76e8554ae","tid":111551,"uid":65818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T13:10:20.000Z","msg":"Point 1: 青春<br />\n你唔拍拖唔會老架咩？<br />\n講青春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男人唔會老？<br />\n男人老左用錢溝女其實女都得<br />\n<br />\nPoint 2: AA制<br />\n老實講你係有本事有廉恥有骨氣就唔洗人主動叫你俾錢嘅<br />\n幫你老母家教你啫<br />\n咩男人屌女人就要付出金錢<br />\n叫雞咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPoint 3: 各取所需又話咩男要大波靚女女要錢各取所需<br />\n你痴撚左線<br />\n自己天生雞格想做雞以為自己想拍拖<br />\n<br />\n結論:<br />\n我唔期望你夠IQ理解你錯咩(如果你夠就唔會錯啦)<br />\n但希望你唔好諗到呢個世界個個都係你咁扭曲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n祝 早日康復<br />\n180 30分的那人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7c4d56379957f8eedecfdcc5ac80857d30940a","tid":111551,"uid":65818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T13:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e527b1a02c0be8d2c86703f1698f2a470073d1","tid":111551,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T13:18:45